      • loadFromClassName

        public CliPluginMetadata loadFromClassName(java.lang.String pluginClassName,
                                           java.lang.String pluginNameOverride)
                                    throws CliRunnerException
        Parameters:
        pluginClassName - string name specifying a plugin to be loaded as of this writing, this is the fully-qualified class name of the plugin class to be loaded; class must be in java's CLASSPATH
        pluginNameOverride - user override of the plugin's "name" (i.e., the value to be returned by the "getName()" method from the plugin metadata), will be null if no override given
        Returns:
        cliPluginMetadata metadata for the CLI plugin that was loaded
        Throws:
        CliRunnerException - unhandled exception thrown while attempting to load plugin

      • loadFromInstance

        public CliPluginMetadata loadFromInstance(java.lang.Object pluginInstance,
                                          java.lang.String pluginNameOverride)
                                   throws CliRunnerException
        Parameters:
        pluginInstance - object instance for whom CliPluginMetadata is being requested
        pluginNameOverride - user override of the plugin's "name" (i.e., the value to be returned by the "getName()" method from the plugin metadata), will be null if no override given
        Returns:
        CliPluginMetadata metadata regarding loaded CLI plugin
        Throws:
        CliRunnerException - thrown if could not load CliPluginMetadata for specified pluginInstance for any reason

      • initializePlugin

        public void initializePlugin(CliPluginMetadata cliPluginMetadata)
                      throws CliRunnerException
        Parameters:
        cliPluginMetadata - metadata for CLI plugin to initialize
        Throws:
        CliRunnerException - unhandled exception thrown by any of the initialization methods of the plugin; NOTE: if thrown, some initialization methods may not get invoked

      • finalizePlugin

        public void finalizePlugin(CliPluginMetadata cliPluginMetadata)
                    throws CliRunnerException
        Calls the "finalizer" method(s) of thespecified CLI plugin
        Parameters:
        cliPluginMetadata - metadata for CLI plugin to finalize
        Throws:
        CliRunnerException - unhandled exception thrown by any of the finalization methods of the plugin; NOTE: if thrown, some finalization methods may not get invoked
